2008", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="The Sieve email filtering language spamtest, spamtestplus, and virustest extensions permit users to use simple, portable commands for spam and virus tests on email messages.  Each extension provides a new test using matches against numeric scores.  It is the responsibility of the underlying Sieve implementation to do the actual checks that result in proper input to the tests. [STANDARDS-TRACK]", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

