2004", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC3685.html", target="_top", tooltip="The SIEVE mail filtering language spamtest and virustest extensions permit users to use simple, portable commands for spam and virus tests on email messages.  Each extension provides a new test using matches against numeric 'scores'.  It is the responsibility of the underlying SIEVE implementation to do the actual checks that result in values returned by the tests. [PROPOSED STANDARD]"];
